## Description {#details}

An entry in either debug&#95;frame or eh&#95;frame.

This entry can be a <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/dwarf/cie">CIE</a> or an <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/dwarf/fde">FDE</a>.

Definition at line 532 of file <a href="/docs/api/files/include/include/llvm/include/llvm/debuginfo/include/llvm/debuginfo/dwarf/dwarfdebugframe-h">DWARFDebugFrame.h</a>.
